SHREK IS LOVE SHREK IS LIFE

Shrek Haven

Hey Coder Broz, Im Shrek, a partner with Coder Broz. I help Coder Broz by promoting the website in discord as well as being a major role in trying to swing important decisions for the best. Currently, Im not the best coder however Im learning HTML and other languages to create fun and interactive experiences. Im excited about the potential of this partnership, I believe I will bring great ideas to Coder Broz such as games, videos, podcasts, merch, and other projects. This website is just the start of something big, the foundation, the building blocks of something incredible. The developers are putting in a lot of effort in every line of code just to please the player. I hope you appreciate the Coder Broz staff and are excited to be a part of this project. Now, to the Shrek stuff. Shrek Haven is a discord server and a website (which was merged with Coder Broz). The Shrekites are a communist society that roams around my majestic swamp. Our little community hosts fun games, stream games, give out candy, take polls, and interact with a variety of bots. We highly encourage you to join our server and worship Shrek.
